84
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:27,590
Everyone likes your talent.

85
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:33,122
However, if all you do is acommodate Neil,

86
00:09:33,122 --> 00:09:36,967
then you will lose your original self.

87
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:41,055
Most importantly,

88
00:09:41,917 --> 00:09:48,675
try believing that this mini album
will be great because of you.

89
00:09:51,792 --> 00:09:55,467
Believe in yourself. You can do it.

