144
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:33,400
Kiddo...

145
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:34,750
Hey, don't drink.

146
00:15:34,750 --> 00:15:36,750
Neil.

147
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:38,792
- Buddies, huh?
- Stop drinking.

148
00:15:38,792 --> 00:15:41,285
