- Great...

149
00:15:41,285 --> 00:15:42,960
Nice... Orca.

150
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:45,667
Hi, I'm Liang.

151
00:15:45,667 --> 00:15:47,375
- Nice to meet you.
- Hey.

152
00:15:47,375 --> 00:15:49,958
You're... my idol.

153
00:15:49,958 --> 00:15:52,417
I'm a big fan.

154
00:15:52,417 --> 00:15:53,792
