155
00:15:53,792 --> 00:15:55,750
So happy, oh happy...

156
00:15:55,750 --> 00:15:57,883
Nice to meet you...

157
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:20,083
Orca hasn't led you astray, right?

158
00:16:20,083 --> 00:16:22,967
We were just talking about music.

159
00:16:23,958 --> 00:16:26,583
Talking about music is dangerous.

160
00:16:26,583 --> 00:16:28,467
Hang tight.

161
00:16:30,667 --> 00:16:33,800
I fell in love with you just by
watching you play the piano.

162
00:16:47,792 --> 00:16:49,967
Orca told me,

163
00:16:51,958 --> 00:16:55,417
I shouldn't write something
you would normally sing.

164
00:16:55,417 --> 00:16:58,508
I should write my own song.

165
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:06,766
He's right.

166
00:17:07,783 --> 00:17:10,749
Just be yourself.

167
00:17:12,098 --> 00:17:13,940
I'll try my best.

168
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:16,584
Not quite right.

169
00:17:16,584 --> 00:17:18,967
We are doing this together.

170
00:17:36,042 --> 00:17:39,083
Let's not practice tomorrow, alright?

171
00:17:39,083 --> 00:17:40,800
Why?

172
00:17:42,417 --> 00:17:44,925
I wanna have a date with you.

173
00:18:38,250 --> 00:18:40,467
Why are you drinking again?

174
00:19:28,417 --> 00:19:30,508
I'm sorry.

175
00:19:31,250 --> 00:19:33,467
It's alright, Reese.

176
00:20:26,292 --> 00:20:28,508
