yet you still like me so much.

178
00:20:40,273 --> 00:20:43,925
I'm sorry. You must be really upset.

179
00:20:49,158 --> 00:20:51,124
You know?

180
00:20:52,083 --> 00:20:55,175
To be honest, I really like you, too.

181
00:20:59,792 --> 00:21:03,675
Because I'm so afraid of losing.

182
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:11,798
So, let's be friends forever.

183
00:21:25,042 --> 00:21:26,842
