205
00:23:38,917 --> 00:23:44,467
Is it impossible between us?

206
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:50,717
Considering all aspects,
it's just not possible.

207
00:23:58,080 --> 00:24:00,667
Look how far we are.

208
00:24:00,667 --> 00:24:04,842
2,260 kilometers is just too far.

209
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:12,375
One flight takes four hours
and costs twenty thousand.

210
00:24:12,375 --> 00:24:15,417
That's 240,000 a year.
It's not cost-effective.

211
00:24:15,417 --> 00:24:17,050
And you.

212
00:24:17,050 --> 00:24:20,292
Orca, love-struck.

213
00:24:20,292 --> 00:24:22,542
I'm quite rational.

214
00:24:22,542 --> 00:24:24,842
We will definitely fight.

215
00:24:26,042 --> 00:24:30,008
Have we fought before?

216
00:24:30,792 --> 00:24:34,333
During those six years, I've explained
a lot to you why we couldn't be together.

217
00:24:34,333 --> 00:24:35,917
How come you don't get it?

218
00:24:35,917 --> 00:24:38,292
Don't you think we have poor communication?

219
00:24:38,292 --> 00:24:42,417
Besides, I have to spend
240,000 a year to learn Thai.

220
00:24:42,417 --> 00:24:44,425
