221
00:24:46,208 --> 00:24:50,092
Then learn it from me.
I can teach you, free of charge.

222
00:24:51,280 --> 00:24:53,330
Most importantly,

223
00:24:54,708 --> 00:24:57,292
I treat you as my brother.

224
00:24:57,292 --> 00:24:59,633
I don't believe it.

225
00:25:01,500 --> 00:25:04,883
